channel.title: [PI] Tyreatta-Scape Release [UPDATED!] [PI]
channel.description:
[center][size=24pt][b]T Y R E A T T A - [/b][b]S C A P E[/b][/size][/center]
EDIT: UPDATES = REUPLOADED with ring of wealth fix, dragon boots dropped by all npcs fixed, added 2 starters per ip, removed 500m on login glitch, different antileech thats less confusing, hint for antileech removed as its really easy. Removed tutorial island and moved guide to different starting location.
Home Area: [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/2z6toab.jpg[/img]
Prestige Shopping: [img]http://i42.tinypic.com/15xvgaf.jpg[/img]
Fun PK: [img]http://i43.tinypic.com/or2jb8.jpg[/img]
Donor Zone: [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/1pukw8.jpg[/img]
Newest Boss [img]http://i44.tinypic.com/3347qkg.jpg[/img]
Points Shop! [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/15q5hjn.jpg[/img]
Clue Scrolls! Easy to add more. [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/29vm7pc.jpg[/img]
Custom Boss I made (Basically just a really powerful mithril dragon with good drops + good drop rarity) [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/2hmh2ko.jpg[/img]
Skills go to 125! [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/2upw8xu.jpg[/img]
Nex, Nothing special. [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/25p67nm.jpg[/img]
Server Announcements on Rare Drops [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/10nzzap.jpg[/img]
Working Ring of wealth [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/1zfsv1e.jpg[/img]
[size=14pt]Features of Tyreatta-Scape:[/size]
- TWO worlds: To get a second world, simply copy the source folder, change the listener port to 43595 in the copied one, run them both and you're done! - 24 fully working skills - Skills go up to level 125! - Squeal of Fortune operational: 3 spins given for each 99, 5 spins for a 125. - X bones on altar - Working ring of wealth! - Portals minigame gives 3m reward for players 5m for donators. - Working commands such as ::home, ::funpk, ::chill, and much more. - Ring of recoil fully working - Crystal keys for crystal chests - 8 working minigames: Duel Arena, Barrows, Pest Control, Tzhaar, Warriors Guild, Assault & Domination, Nomad & Angry Goblin, Portals Minigame. - Loyalty points with shop - Double XP ring in loyalty shop - Minecraft gear in loyalty shop - Enable/Disable x10 hitting - Enable/Disable New HP bar - All working emotions - ::yell feature for all players - 2 Training areas - Prestige levels with prestige points - Rare drop table, with caskets, crystal keys, d boots. - Another drop table with a high rarity containing red, yellow and blue reward tokens, the red reward tokens can only be recieved as a drop if you are a donator. Yellow and Blue give either SOF spins or tyreatta-scape points, the read gives donator chest points. - Tutorial island for new players, starting items added to bank - Secured banks with bank pins
List of things I can remember that I did.
[code]1. Re-Enabled item dropping 2. Fixed barrows minimap 3. Made 2 worlds on different servers 4. Added working ring of wealth 5. Added forgotten warrior that drops primal 6. Added clue scrolls!! 7. Fixed loyalty shop giving double xp ring instead of death cape 8. Fixed staff tab a bit 9. Fixed staff being unable to teleport to donator zone 10. Added Npc Dicing 11. Fixed a few items from crystal key chest. 12. Added crystal keys to random drop table. 13. Added key chest to home. 14. Fixed dungeoneering bug where you couldnt finish it. 15. Added extra rare drops only for donators 16. Fixed Steadfast, Ragefire and glaiven boots. 17. Added custom boss (in boss tele) 18. Fixed Polypore staff 19. Added Ganodermic as a drop to mad mummy. 20. Made new gear require a corresponding level of 125 e.g. Range gear requires range lvl of 125 etc.. 21. Gave new boss decent good animations. 22. Made new gear give good bonuses. 23. Made dclaws just a tiny bit better 24. Removed phats and some other shit from ckey chest 25. Added a few better items to donator chest 26. Made donator titles have different colors. Extreme = Purple. Donator = Green 27. Swapped vote points for prestige points 28. Added prestige levels that give a prestige point every time you prestige. 29. Made better ::commands 30. added ::donatorcommands , ::modcommands , ::admincommands , ::ownercommands 31. Fixed levels not going up correctly and saying it was 125 when it was 119. 32. Added rare drop announcements to server. 33. Replaced aura's in loyalty shop 34. Made better thieving 35. Updated commands.java 36. Changed home 37. Fixed royal crossbow 38. Got royal bolts working properly 39. Added bork boss 40. Made bork drop vesta's + stat helm 41 Added control to reply to pm's 42. Fixed all slayer tasks being easy tasks 43. Made royal bolts stackable 44. Added royal bolts and crossbow to pet dragon drops 45. Fixed Gmaul spec! 46. Made thieving give better xp 47. Made thieving give money (based on theiving level) + items. 48. A free slot is required for thieving which prevents autoclicking. 49. Changed starter and made it much better 50. Added portals minigame 51. Added tutorial island with starter items added to bank. 52. Removed some items from shops 53. Increased required levels for woodcutting (better for levels that go to 125) 54. Changed Donator Zone 55. Added Ice Warrior Portal for slayer tasks 56. Made rare drop table a bit better 57. Added second even rarer drop table with reward tokens
[/code]
Credits: Hack3r Sanity Jagex Myself
I had a lot of fun coding this server, I put a lot of time into this, there are a lot of tiny bugs that i fixed and didn't mention above, and some that still need to be fixed. It was a shame that I could no longer host it, due to router issues and personal issues to which I will not mention.
Enjoy.
To make items be announced as a rare drop in config.java look for
[code]public static final int[] ITEM_RARE[/code]
and add the item id there
